{
  "text": "Minimizing long-term pulmonary impairment, and neurologic complications associated with BPD has become the main focus of perinatal care [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Nonetheless, increasing evidence suggests that the early pathologic changes observed in BPD contribute to long-lasting consequences including premature aging of the lung.",
